    {
      "id": "A6EjYs2Dcqb_DSeorUyAW",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 318.20503531236056,
      "y": -20.22796349490588,
      "width": 920.9913940429688,
      "height": 80,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aP",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1780413147,
      "version": 920,
      "versionNonce": 1111389333,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1770993113074,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The main service worker will register under /app and will have sub-routes for ScramJet (/app/~/scram) and Ultraviolet\n(/app/~/uv). Along side the proxy routes, it will also handle the /app/internal/addons/<addonID> route. This route\nwill serve browser cached addon files after they have been proxied and polyfilled through the ScramJetAPI.\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The main service worker will register under /app and will have sub-routes for ScramJet (/app/~/scram) and Ultraviolet\n(/app/~/uv). Along side the proxy routes, it will also handle the /app/internal/addons/<addonID> route. This route\nwill serve browser cached addon files after they have been proxied and polyfilled through the ScramJetAPI.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
